collectionMetadata.name: Polytechnics - Intake, Enrolment and Graduates by Course
collectionMetadata.description:
1) Intake, enrolment and graduate figures refer to full-time diploma courses only. Intake excludes 1,485 students (of which 715 are female) on Polytechnic Foundation Programme.
2) Intake includes direct entry to second year.
3)  Courses are classified according to course content.

datasetMetadata.name: Intake, Enrolment and Graduates of Polytechnics by Course
datasetMetadata.description:
1) Intake, enrolment and graduate figures refer to full-time diploma courses only. Excludes students on Polytechnic Foundation Programme.

2) Intake includes direct entry to second year.

3) Courses are classified according to course content of the highest weighting.
